<para id="element-414">The slope (<emphasis effect="italics">b</emphasis>) can be written as <m:math>
 <m:mrow>
  <m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo>
   <m:mrow>
    <m:mfrac>
     <m:mrow>
      <m:msub>
