<solution id="fs-id1170308849163">
<table id="fs-id1170308849165" summary="This table shows 2 columns. The left column is labeled X SAT math scores. The right column is labeled Y GPA. The first row has an X value of 261 and a Y value of 50. The next row has an X value of 262 and a Y value of 60. The next row has an X value of 327 and a Y value of 62. The next row has an X value of 350 and a Y value of 65. The next row has an X value of 363 and a Y value of 70. The next row has an X value of 364 and a Y value of 67. The next row has an X value of 373 and a Y value of 71. The next row has an X value of 544 and a Y value of 86. The next row has an X value of 587 and a Y value of 87. The next row has an X value of 624 and a Y value of 90. The last row has an X value of 741 and a Y value of 98.">
